WEBVTT

01:28:01.624 --> 01:28:04.749
and I'll never have that recipe again.

01:28:06.666 --> 01:28:09.624
Oh, no.

01:28:11.624 --> 01:28:16.541
I love a good dream sequence.

01:28:18.499 --> 01:28:22.166
There would be another song for me,

01:28:23.374 --> 01:28:27.166
for I will sing it.

01:28:29.666 --> 01:28:32.791
I will drink the wine while it is warm,

01:28:33.374 --> 01:28:38.166
and never let you
catch me looking at the sun.

01:28:41.749 --> 01:28:46.416
And after all the loves of my life,

01:28:47.624 --> 01:28:51.791
after all the loves of my life,

01:28:51.791 --> 01:28:53.374
you'll still be the one.
